WEBVTT

00:01:29.208 --> 00:01:32.184
We have no reason to depend on aid

00:01:32.208 --> 00:01:35.809
or borrowing money
from China or the World Bank.

00:01:35.833 --> 00:01:37.268
But without good leaders,

00:01:37.292 --> 00:01:41.518
we're like an eagle
that has no idea it could fly,

00:01:41.542 --> 00:01:43.351
let alone soar.

00:01:43.375 --> 00:01:45.809
Africa is a like a sleeping giant.

00:01:45.833 --> 00:01:49.184
Now the truth is,
I'm trying to wake up this giant,

00:01:49.208 --> 00:01:51.309
and that's why I air the dirty laundry

00:01:51.333 --> 00:01:53.393
of those in charge of the giant.

00:01:53.417 --> 00:01:56.143
Our politicians, our religious leaders,

00:01:56.167 --> 00:01:57.893
with huge respect, of course,

00:01:57.917 --> 00:02:00.601
